			Decreased mana cost by {1}%
			Increases maximum mana by {2}
			Increases the maximum number of minions by {3}
			Counts as wings
			Summons shadow hands to carry you and attack your foes
			Your attacks are accompanied by multiple magical tomes at half power
			Effects scale with your obesity
			'''
	}

	MeteorCrush: {
		DisplayName: Meteor Crush
		Tooltip: Makes your weight able to crush your enemies
	}

	HoneyedHamBat: {
		DisplayName: Honeyed Ham Bat
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Grows more powerful the more obese you are
